&lt;a href="#%e5%be%85%e5%8a%9e%e4%ba%8b%e9%a1%b9%e6%89%a9%e5%b1%95%e5%85%b3%e9%94%ae%e7%89%b9%e6%80%a7%e9%83%a8%e5%88%86" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>机器学习客户行为模型&lt;/li>
&lt;li>实时客户评分和洞察&lt;/li>
